{"tid":704882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"\"一同拒絕簡體中文資源\" 之台灣人反應, 舔共人士哪來的? 五毛黨? 台灣人愚蠢? 港友如何看?","createTime":"2018-06-16T16:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T17:14:40.000Z","uid":147756,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"16a079daa090b1c5b7c06871bf3e107eb6117824","tid":704882,"uid":147756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【密技】拒絕半強迫查看簡中資源, 自行決定Google搜尋結果(Chrome)</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60030&amp;snA=495832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60030%26snA%3D495832&d=f24UGJmhnatya6gsXmPiZk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=adc6df86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60030&amp;snA=495832</a></span><br />\n<br />\n台灣巴哈姆特不像LIHKG這邊一樣給<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 給得很習慣.<br />\n所以要是真的給出了, 基本上就是完全否定對方才會出現.<br />\n<br />\n目前不知道有多少五毛黨, 或者使用蝗語的人在巴哈活動.<br />\n但這篇文章的部分反應, 很<ins><strong>明顯就是一堆人認為自己死也該看簡體中文資源</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">利申 : <ins>個人不想看到任何簡中資源</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>對此現象, 港友們如何看呢?</strong><br />\n<br />\n台灣人愚蠢 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陸仔, 五毛黨造成的 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a76159ae6446f9806360418989271fa990b8bb3","tid":704882,"uid":147756,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:07:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">二樓問題</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>對於簡體中文(蝗語)網路資源, 港友們如何看呢?</strong><br />\n<br />\n盡量不看, 除非不得已 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無所謂, 知識較重要, 都會看 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b5e3f0368bd00a2e15cbe034db7566e9be9713","tid":70